<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta content="text/html"; charset="UTF-8"; http-equiv="Content Type">
</head>

<body>
	<h1>Welcome to the sample app, <%= @user.name %>!</h1>
	<p>
		Your user name is <%= @user.username %><br \>	
		This email contains the confirmation code to access your profile.<br \>
		Your confirmation code is: <%= @user.gen_code %>. Click on the link to navigate to the sign in page. Once there, sign in and enter the code. Then, you're done! Please beware that this code will expire in one week. If you do not enter the code in that time, please go to the sign up page, and sign up again.<br \>
		Link: <%= link_to "sample_app", signin_path %>
    </p>
		
	<p> Thanks! And have fun!</p>
</body>
</html> 
		
	